1938;;Kidnapped;;American;;Otto Preminger, Alfred L. Werker;;Warner Baxter, Freddie Bartholomew, Reginald Owen;;adventure;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kidnapped_(1938_film);;In 1747, David Balfour's evil uncle arranges for him to be kidnapped and sent to sea where he meets exiled Alan Breck. The two make their way back to Scotland and justice.